description:
It's almost time for the holiday season, and you know what that means: FESTIVE DLC! Decorate for the snowy winter season (apologies to the southern hemisphere) with a big ol' hamper of snowmen, gingerbread, candy canes, and presents to make sure that everyone knows how much you love the holidays. And presents.

This DLC Contains
1 New House Skin - Snowman House
1 New Rug
2 New Snowmen
1 New Snowboard
4 Icicle Variations
name: Moonstone Island: Cozy Comforts DLC Pack
